{"tid":241184,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦壞左請教","createTime":"2017-05-13T03:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T13:20:36.000Z","uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9b7ed3da5ac973234ce84e61fcc0577b80e133","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"滑鼠郁郁下會停左<br />\n之後聽到除usb個兩聲&quot;登櫈&quot;<br />\n之後又繼續用到<br />\n<br />\n但通常開得部機耐<br />\n&quot;登櫈&quot; 幾次後就再用唔返<br />\n要手動reboot <br />\n<br />\n想問部機邊度壞左？<br />\n火牛，底版？或者咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 滑鼠冇壞<br />\n插去其他電腦用足全程<br />\n<br />\n2. 都試過滑鼠插幾他曹<br />\n都有以上問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665fd5865fe3d95a97b75f57d3087fa8180d820c","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>滑鼠郁郁下會停左<br />\n之後聽到除usb個兩聲&quot;登櫈&quot;<br />\n之後又繼續用到<br />\n<br />\n但通常開得部機耐<br />\n&quot;登櫈&quot; 幾次後就再用唔返<br />\n要手動reboot <br />\n<br />\n想問部機邊度壞左？<br />\n火牛，底版？或者咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 滑鼠冇壞<br />\n插去其他電腦用足全程<br />\n<br />\n2. 都試過滑鼠插幾他曹<br />\n都有以上問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMB壞"},{"pid":"71fee710edea526fac98cb57df92cabb7ca67bfb","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window"},{"pid":"aed04f984361359c4d768e30a17c40113f7c221f","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>滑鼠郁郁下會停左<br />\n之後聽到除usb個兩聲&quot;登櫈&quot;<br />\n之後又繼續用到<br />\n<br />\n但通常開得部機耐<br />\n&quot;登櫈&quot; 幾次後就再用唔返<br />\n要手動reboot <br />\n<br />\n想問部機邊度壞左？<br />\n火牛，底版？或者咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 滑鼠冇壞<br />\n插去其他電腦用足全程<br />\n<br />\n2. 都試過滑鼠插幾他曹<br />\n都有以上問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMB壞</blockquote><br />\n咁我淨係買塊底版<br />\n其他野用返舊就得？"},{"pid":"565a9259d77d45d7f85aeb2cdcf9516af3bd72b9","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620b547a6c2eb50b53be4d136d3475847559f74e","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲"},{"pid":"b4296a5fae5bb2db38a73870edaf67958f0328c2","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e8e7ddc9c4efcabec0fbd448a758262bcc2990","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？"},{"pid":"c0fc22f1ce73b2f784e1cab2c4f90cd492d6223e","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗"},{"pid":"6549c43e76b20dd21b715befa2ba4d301b692870","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPort槽連住MB 多數MB都係咁好似係"},{"pid":"035f3fec1e2d1ff4975c2527d5a7ea06e6f04493","tid":241184,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPort槽連住MB 多數MB都係咁好似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔得就買過塊MB唔洗煩"},{"pid":"5203d80bbc4dec153d527aa36b57b4d6c5955cd5","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPort槽連住MB 多數MB都係咁好似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔得就買過塊MB唔洗煩</blockquote><br />\n買塊版使唔使一千<br />\n<br />\n其實呢部野都用左6年<br />\n都想砌返部<br />\n但呢幾年間唔中都有換過野<br />\n<br />\n換過牛，ram, hdd <br />\n所以又唔知使唔使砌部新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bbe6fe3a058b14465442a798197c7379bb9618","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPort槽連住MB 多數MB都係咁好似係</blockquote><br />\n我d槽係連底版<br />\n<br />\n如果我買左版返黎但發現唔係壞佢咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a513e537569b511139a5df98c74eccc335fbb6d5","tid":241184,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都有可能係軟件撞左，壞window</blockquote><br />\n呢個情況係咪洗機就解決到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPort槽連住MB 多數MB都係咁好似係</blockquote><br />\n我d槽係連底版<br />\n<br />\n如果我買左版返黎但發現唔係壞佢咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪多咗塊板做後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a2d0f3b2928a29209170b9c38d94f2044c7b80","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係window壞，就重裝就得<br />\nMB壞就麻煩d， 唔知會唔會關你d port位事，重裝左先再睇。<br />\n我覺得似window壞多d，就咁聽你講，多數MB一壞就點插都用唔到，同埋無登登聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能只係你port槽壞又唔奇，硬件壞太多可能性答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但port 槽壞可以就咁換？<br />\n<br />\n或者我而家係咪應該洗機再試一試先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕煩就洗機試左先，唔得再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPort槽連住MB 多數MB都係咁好似係</blockquote><br />\n我d槽係連底版<br />\n<br />\n如果我買左版返黎但發現唔係壞佢咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪多咗塊板做後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁之後又要再換真係壞左個樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e006aefccb64fbe7aca5545e9133950abb74ea4","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f996b5f0a89f43982227653c8070071de0723f62","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39cb73aa5cd41e66a46aad69f7f2b478b2c94ce","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6cde3be7ad3b8d3959e5f81307f021a69a8877","tid":241184,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}